summary: A female version of General Tullius. Replaces both the main and Civil War Battle version of Tullius.
descriptionHtml:
Basically, this is a female version of General Tullius replacing both the version of him when he's in the civil war and when he's in Castle Dour.

I created this mod out of boredom so the first version isn't anything special however the versions following will have voice acting and other things that will be added when I think of them.

If you do want to voice act the female version of General Tullius contact me.

If you want to help me create mods faster go check out my [url=https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKRSTAVemC9Kwt-6QeGZw2g]YouTube Channel[/url]

Edit: I know I have terrible shading and textures.
author: AUDelusional
